<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="aioseo-method-2-add-a-fundraising-thermometer-with-the-donation-thermometer-plugin-best-free-option">Method 2: Add a Fundraising Thermometer With the Donation Thermometer Plugin (Best Free Option)</h4>



<p>If you just want a quick and free way to show your fundraising progress, then the <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/donation-thermometer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" title="Donation Thermometer">Donation Thermometer</a> plugin is a great pick. </p>



