<p>I recommend this method for small community fundraisers, school projects, or personal charity drives that don‚Äôt require features like donor tracking or payment integrations.</p>



<h5 class="wp-block-heading" id="aioseo-step-1">Step 1: Install and Activate the Donation Thermometer Plugin</h5>



<p>You can start by installing and activating the <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/donation-thermometer" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" title="Donation Thermometer">Donation Thermometer</a> plugin. </p>



