<h5 class="wp-block-heading" id="aioseo-step-2">Step 2: Set Your Fundraising Targets</h5>



<p>Upon plugin activation, go to the <strong>Settings ¬ª Thermometer</strong> page from your WordPress dashboard. Here, you will set up the goal for your fundraising thermometer.</p>



<p>In the &#8216;Thermometer Values&#8217; section, start by entering your &#8216;Target Value&#8217;. This is the total amount you want to raise for your campaign (for example, 50000).</p>



<p>Next, enter your &#8216;Raised Value&#8217;, which shows how much has already been collected (for example, 25000). If you haven‚Äôt raised any money yet, you can leave this field blank for now. </p>



