<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="352" src="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/configure-entry-status-as-approved-in-formidable-forms.png" alt="Configure entry status as approved in Formidable Forms" class="wp-image-370246" srcset="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/configure-entry-status-as-approved-in-formidable-forms.png 680w, https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/configure-entry-status-as-approved-in-formidable-forms-300x155.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure>



<p>Next, go back to the <strong>Formidable ¬ª Applications</strong> page. Now it‚Äôs time to customize your Charity Donation Thermometer Progress Bar.</p>



