<p>Click the &#8216;Edit&#8217; link under the Charity Donation Thermometer Progress Bar.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="265" src="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/click-edit-under-donation-thermometer-progress-bar-in-formidable-forms.png" alt="Click the Edit link under Donation Thermometer Progress Bar" class="wp-image-370247" srcset="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/click-edit-under-donation-thermometer-progress-bar-in-formidable-forms.png 680w, https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/click-edit-under-donation-thermometer-progress-bar-in-formidable-forms-300x117.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure>



<p>This will open the Formidable Views builder, where you can adjust the thermometer‚Äôs appearance. </p>



