<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="351" src="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/customize-fundraising-thermometer-in-formidable-forms.png" alt="Customize the fundraising thermometer in Formidable Forms" class="wp-image-370248" srcset="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/customize-fundraising-thermometer-in-formidable-forms.png 680w, https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/customize-fundraising-thermometer-in-formidable-forms-300x155.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></figure>



